## Story and assets

The story written for this game and the various assets are licensed under CreativeCommons Attribution ShareAlike 4.0

This cover the following files :

- `sql/*.csv`
- `static/img/**`

Exception for the assets that originate from the Fallout games which are copyrighted by Bethesda and included under [fair use](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fair_use) terms, such as :

- `static/img/back/holotape.jpg`
- `static/img/back/brotherhood.png`
- `static/img/aid/rad-x.png`
- `static/img/aid/stimpak.png`
- `static/img/misc/mininuke.png`

